# CODEOWNERS — auto-assign reviewers on every PR.
#
# Syntax: <path pattern>  <owner...>  (https://docs.github.com/repos/codeowners)
# The last matching pattern wins, so put narrower rules below broader ones.

# Catch-all: @Antoinegtir reviews everything by default.
*                                       @Antoinegtir

# Build / release plumbing — keep the maintainer in the loop on any
# change that affects how binaries get cut.
/.github/workflows/                     @Antoinegtir
/Dockerfile                             @Antoinegtir
/.dockerignore                          @Antoinegtir
/install.sh                             @Antoinegtir
/uninstall.sh                           @Antoinegtir

# Security / policy docs.
/SECURITY.md                            @Antoinegtir
/.github/CODEOWNERS                     @Antoinegtir
